  "date": "2026-06-02 17:00:00",
  "author": "十字路口Crossing",
  "siteName": "十字路口Crossing",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <div style=\"word-wrap:break-word;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, 'PingFang SC', Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, 'Times New Roman', serif;line-height:1.75;\">\n   <div style=\"word-wrap:break-word;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, 'PingFang SC', Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, 'Times New Roman', serif;line-height:1.75;\">\n    <p style=\"border-top:none;padding:10px;border-right:none;margin:20px 0;color:#407600;display:block;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;line-height:26px;border-bottom:none;word-spacing:normal;outline:0;overflow:auto;max-width:100%;border-left:3px solid #407600;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, 'PingFang SC', Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, 'Times New Roman', serif;hyphens:auto;text-align:left;\"><strong style=\"word-break: break-all;font-weight: 600;color: #407600;\"><span>我把 Codex 接进了扣子 3.0，搭了 Shopify 电商 Agent Team。</span></strong></p>\n    <p style=\"margin: 15px 0;text-align: center;\"><img alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" style=\"max-width: 100%;border-radius: 10px;display: inline-block;height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=4aaa0d52&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2Fa16Y4PLxPqmBEIWCtYrLYUhCa8JibiazKkeB5x2iaicCxsHo1fDmRsEvoftm7iaDQnpDIX3FrTqQU6nUVFuMm3etOpNj4wFBRUh80R2BibHkudgdU%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n    <p style=\"margin:0px;white-space:pre-line;letter-spacing:0.1em;padding-bottom:1em;font-size:15px;line-height:26px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;text-align:right;\"><span>👦🏻 作者: GaKi</span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin:0px;white-space:pre-line;letter-spacing:0.1em;padding-bottom:1em;font-size:15px;line-height:26px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;text-align:right;\"><span>🥷 编辑: Koji</span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin:0px;white-space:pre-line;letter-spacing:0.1em;padding-bottom:1em;font-size:15px;line-height:26px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;text-align:right;\"><span>🧑‍🎨 排版: NCon</span></p>\n   </div>\n   <p style=\"margin: 15px 0;text-align: center;\"><img alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" style=\"max-width: 100%;border-radius: 10px;display: inline-block;height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=fe2898ea&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2Fa16Y4PLxPqmiaIFYSvQxZJ2MYq0eOJQKytJQB6OYHn7bdg5LfJ4oWGBlw9lXRFLqzUeSfWIncNVwwlXIl22F1QpNmdeZTkJ2RQFMibxdhftwk%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n   <p style=\"border:1px solid #407600;border-radius:8px;padding:16px 20px;margin:20px 0;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, 'PingFang SC', Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, 'Times New Roman', serif;line-height:26px;\"><span>昨天，</span><strong style=\"word-break: break-all;font-weight: 600;color: #407600;\"><span>扣子正式升级到 3.0</span></strong><span>。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin:0;white-space:pre-line;letter-spacing:0.1em;padding-bottom:1em;font-size:15px;line-height:26px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, 'PingFang SC', Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, 'Times New Roman', serif;text-align:left;\"><span>「十字路口」团队第一时间做了实测，这次更新的内容还是比较多的——</span><strong style=\"word-break: break-all;font-weight: 600;color: #407600;\"><span>Agent Team 协作、本地 Agent</span></strong><span>&nbsp;等多个能力同步上线，整体界面也做了重构。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 15px 0;text-align: center;\"><img alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" style=\"max-width: 100%;border-radius: 10px;display: inline-block;height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=1da39bcf&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2Fa16Y4PLxPqkf6c7oTZ2PjOlxXy9IysIZ6s18eSgWq2xu84CQaUT3icC5xn0iabvpHiaawChKl2ktVSA0U4Vqian2Q8RJ9HVpCWnOicxb0oDDJiavM%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n   <p style=\"margin:0;white-space:pre-line;letter-spacing:0.1em;padding-bottom:1em;font-size:15px;line-height:26px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, 'PingFang SC', Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, 'Times New Roman', serif;text-align:left;\"><span>官方有一句很有「画面感」的介绍：在扣子 3.0 里，你可以组建一整个 Agent Team，</span><strong style=\"word-break: break-all;font-weight: 600;color: #407600;\"><span>@ 一下，全员就位。</span></strong><span>可以说，这是一次名副其实的大版本更新了。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin:0;white-space:pre-line;letter-spacing:0.1em;padding-bottom:1em;font-size:15px;line-height:26px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, 'PingFang SC', Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, 'Times New Roman', serif;text-align:left;\"><span>在展开 3.0 的细节之前，扣子这两年多的更新节奏，值得单独聊聊。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin:0;white-space:pre-line;letter-spacing:0.1em;padding-bottom:1em;font-size:15px;line-height:26px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, 'PingFang SC', Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, 'Times New Roman', serif;text-align:left;\"><span>2024 年 2 月 1 日，扣子国内版正式上线，当天流量爆表，服务器一度被挤垮。一年之后，2025 年 4 月，扣子空间推出，产品开始向个人工作场景延伸，邀请码一度刷屏。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin:0;white-space:pre-line;letter-spacing:0.1em;padding-bottom:1em;font-size:15px;line-height:26px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, 'PingFang SC', Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, 'Times New Roman', serif;text-align:left;\"><span>进入 2026 年，节奏明显加快。1 月 19 日，2.0 上线，核心是让 Agent 真正\"能干活\"，引入了长期计划与技能封装的概念；4 月 7 日，2.5 紧接着上线，给 Agent 配上了云电脑和云手机，让它能在真实系统环境里处理文件、操作 App；到了 5 月 25 日，3.0 进入内测，试图让</span><strong style=\"word-break: break-all;font-weight: 600;color: #407600;\"><span>多 Agent 协作体系</span></strong><span>落地。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin:0;white-space:pre-line;letter-spacing:0.1em;padding-bottom:1em;font-size:15px;line-height:26px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, 'PingFang SC', Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, 'Times New Roman', serif;text-align:left;\"><span>值得注意的是：</span></p>\n   <p style=\"border:1px solid #407600;border-radius:8px;padding:16px 20px;margin:20px 0;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, 'PingFang SC', Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, 'Times New Roman', serif;line-height:26px;\"><span>2.0 到 2.5 之间隔了 78 天，而 2.5 到 3.0，只用了 48 天。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin:0;white-space:pre-line;letter-spacing:0.1em;padding-bottom:1em;font-size:15px;line-height:26px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, 'PingFang SC', Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, 'Times New Roman', serif;text-align:left;\"><strong style=\"word-break: break-all;font-weight: 600;color: #407600;\"><span>先让 Agent 能干活，再给 Agent 配工具，最后让多个 Agent 互相配合</span></strong><span>是这几个多版本更新的基础逻辑线。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"border-top:none;padding:10px;border-right:none;margin:20px 0;color:#407600;display:block;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;line-height:26px;border-bottom:none;word-spacing:normal;outline:0;overflow:auto;max-width:100%;border-left:3px solid #407600;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, 'PingFang SC', Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, 'Times New Roman', serif;hyphens:auto;text-align:left;\"><span>先把产品推出去，跟着真实用户反馈持续校准，不死等所谓的「完美版本」。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin:0;white-space:pre-line;letter-spacing:0.1em;padding-bottom:1em;font-size:15px;line-height:26px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, 'PingFang SC', Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, 'Times New Roman', serif;text-align:left;\"><span>这种打法，非常「扣子」。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin:40px 0;font-weight:bold;display:block;width:fit-content;font-size:17px;line-height:1.5;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, 'PingFang SC', Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, 'Times New Roman', serif;text-align:left;\"><span>🚥</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin:0;white-space:pre-line;letter-spacing:0.1em;padding-bottom:1em;font-size:15px;line-height:26px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, 'PingFang SC', Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, 'Times New Roman', serif;text-align:left;\"><span>接下来，分享我们的完整实测体验。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"display: block;line-height: 1.5;font-size: 24px;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, 'PingFang SC', Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, 'Times New Roman', serif;font-weight: bold;margin: 80px auto 40px auto;width: fit-content;color: #407600;text-align: center;padding: 0 1em;border-bottom: 8px solid #407600;\"><span>我把 Codex 接进了扣子 3.0，搭了 Shopify 电商 Agent Team</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin:0;white-space:pre-line;letter-spacing:0.1em;padding-bottom:1em;font-size:15px;line-height:26px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, 'PingFang SC', Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, 'Times New Roman', serif;text-align:left;\"><span>这次更新涉及的内容比较多，我跑了一个相对完整的工作流去测，把这次更新到的功能基本都覆盖了一遍。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin:0;white-space:pre-line;letter-spacing:0.1em;padding-bottom:1em;font-size:15px;line-height:26px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, 'PingFang SC', Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, 'Times New Roman', serif;text-align:left;\"><span>这个案例本身对我也算是一个真实的工作需求，很多团队一直想做自己的周边电商，但内部并没有专职的选品、企划、外贸团队，这种情况下，能不能用一组 Agent 把前期的调研到 Shopify 店铺原型搭建这一段跑通，是我比较好奇的事。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin:0;white-space:pre-line;letter-spacing:0.1em;padding-bottom:1em;font-size:15px;line-height:26px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, 'PingFang SC', Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, 'Times New Roman', serif;text-align:left;\"><span>整体思路是：</span></p>\n   <p style=\"border:1px solid #407600;border-radius:8px;padding:16px 20px;margin:20px 0;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, 'PingFang SC', Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, 'Times New Roman', serif;line-height:26px;\"><strong style=\"word-break: break-all;font-weight: 600;color: #407600;\"><span>在扣子里组一个 Agent Team，上传「十字路口」的团队定位，让它先做小红书每日风向的调研、确定相关的风格元素，再进入外贸电商的选品调研，接着出商品企划，最后通过本地接入的 Codex，根据前面这一整套调研报告，快速搭出一个独立站的原型。</span></strong></p>\n   <p style=\"margin:0;white-space:pre-line;letter-spacing:0.1em;padding-bottom:1em;font-size:15px;line-height:26px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, 'PingFang SC', Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, 'Times New Roman', serif;text-align:left;\"><span>整体看，扣子 3.0 这次界面做了重构，工作流的起点也从原来的对话形式，换成了以项目为单位。左上角可以直接新建一个项目，也可以先把要用到的 Agent 都建好。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 15px 0;text-align: center;\"><img alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" style=\"max-width: 100%;border-radius: 10px;display: inline-block;height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=f5ba3a07&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2Fa16Y4PLxPqkDtKAjIkHVVUnjiab6iaoKR1vicLIcPO20SJnD5jJ9t788uFx0RGkB07OwicWxekZB8l0k80wQqjBDJAvEHpicSP0gqkLZeSeC9RYw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n   <p style=\"margin:0;white-space:pre-line;letter-spacing:0.1em;padding-bottom:1em;font-size:15px;line-height:26px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, 'PingFang SC', Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, 'Times New Roman', serif;text-align:left;\"><span>建 Agent 有两条路径，一种是新建云端 Agent，另一种是把本地的 Claude Code、Codex、OpenClaw 接进来。云端 Agent 的创建比较直接，写好名称就行。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin:0;white-space:pre-line;letter-spacing:0.1em;padding-bottom:1em;font-size:15px;line-height:26px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, 'PingFang SC', Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, 'Times New Roman', serif;text-align:left;\"><span>在我这个工作流里，先按节点把要做的事情拆开，大致分成：</span></p>\n   <p style=\"border:1px solid #407600;border-radius:8px;padding:16px 20px;margin:20px 0;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, 'PingFang SC', Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, 'Times New Roman', serif;line-height:26px;\"><strong style=\"word-break: break-all;font-weight: 600;color: #407600;\"><span>小红书风向标调研 Agent、外贸爆品调研 Agent、商品企划 Agent，再加一个由 Codex 组成的编程 Agent。</span></strong></p>\n   <p style=\"margin:0;white-space:pre-line;letter-spacing:0.1em;padding-bottom:1em;font-size:15px;line-height:26px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, 'PingFang SC', Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, 'Times New Roman', serif;text-align:left;\"><span>在这几个子 Agent 之上，</span><strong style=\"word-break: break-all;font-weight: 600;color: #407600;\"><span>再设了一个主 Agent</span></strong><span>，负责统筹整个 Agent Team。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin:0;white-space:pre-line;letter-spacing:0.1em;padding-bottom:1em;font-size:15px;line-height:26px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, 'PingFang SC', Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, 'Times New Roman', serif;text-align:left;\"><span>这个拆法基本上就是主 Agent 相当于项目负责人，下面三个子 Agent 各管一个部分，编程 Agent 是网站原型快速落地的一环。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 15px 0;text-align: center;\"><img alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" style=\"max-width: 100%;border-radius: 10px;display: inline-block;height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=d3d2b09e&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2Fa16Y4PLxPqksA5AYpic533icjAfuQeGV13DibE3AZMKlBeEy6UuFwuZicwuic0IicfhIFVDRc5b8LDjDqy5grlg1zkCDicu08ibjQjKafMSclrEcYTY%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n   <p style=\"margin:0;white-space:pre-line;letter-spacing:0.1em;padding-bottom:1em;font-size:15px;line-height:26px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, 'PingFang SC', Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, 'Times New Roman', serif;text-align:left;\"><span>每个 Agent 建出来之后，默认就带一组基础技能，需要的话可以再继续添加，模型是可以自定义的：</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 15px 0;text-align: center;\"><img alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" style=\"max-width: 100%;border-radius: 10px;display: inline-block;height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=c5f408ae&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2Fa16Y4PLxPqlvBLMeqZiax1fxkdmicAXO29tkZOF8Bia3R8Zpn7ZOEpnZmKNrGxkIpAxJcoLgqBfTia2hK2wzX6tic6tBJom4kehWiaFibjq0OVeRPA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n   <p style=\"margin:0;white-space:pre-line;letter-spacing:0.1em;padding-bottom:1em;font-size:15px;line-height:26px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, 'PingFang SC', Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, 'Times New Roman', serif;text-align:left;\"><span>在添加技能这一步，可以看到 Agent 市场里已经封装好的技能数量挺多的：</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 15px 0;text-align: center;\"><img alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" style=\"max-width: 100%;border-radius: 10px;display: inline-block;height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=0d26422b&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2Fa16Y4PLxPqmiacmS9TGyoYWodjbMuNXpdJVaTMlqOp4sG4icFMYe9zWKGianHj6FBRUlrKSQWzp4aDfAkO2II43hlc38EWNIkVibQ1p6OqRoRRk%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n   <p style=\"margin:0;white-space:pre-line;letter-spacing:0.1em;padding-bottom:1em;font-size:15px;line-height:26px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, 'PingFang SC', Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, 'Times New Roman', serif;text-align:left;\"><span>需要哪一个就直接一键加上。比如小红书风向标调研 Agent 这条线，我给它配了热门账号推荐、爆款笔记、每日爆